  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſchee Pilsfahti laid\njums par Gelbefchannu irr/ no ta\nAtreebeja/ ka taim Nokawejam/\nlas zittu netiſchſchu nekawis ne\nirr jamirſt/ teekams wiꞥſch\npreekſch tahs Draudses Sohdá\nſtahw.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ſchee Pilsfahti/ ko juhs\ndohſeet/ laid irr ſesch Gelbefcha-\nnas-Pilsfahti preekſch jums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Trihs no ſcheem Pilsfah-\nteem buhs jums doht ſchaf Jar-\ndanas Puﬀê/ un trihs no teem\nPilsfahteem buhs doht ceſſch Ra-\nnaana Seimnes/ Gelbefchanas-\nPilsfahteem buhs teem buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee Pilsfahti laid irr\nkeein Israëta Behrneem par Gel-\nbeſchann/ ir taim Sweschinee-\nkam/ir taim Peedſihwotajam juh-\nfu Starpâ/ ka us turren behgt\nwarr ikkatrs/ kas kahdu Ziliweku\nnonejanſchu nokawis irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet ja wiꞥſch to ar kahdu\nDselsa Rihku ſittis irr/ ka wiꞥſch\nmirſt/ tas irr weens Slepkawe/\nſchim Slepkavam buhs nokan-\ntam tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jeb ja wiꞥſch to ar Akimi-\nni Rohkâ/ zaur ko kas warr nok-\nkauts tapt/ ſitt/ ka tas mirſt/ tas\nirr Slepkawe/ tam buhs nokan-\ntam tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jeb ja wiꞥſch to ar kahdu\nRohka Gabbalu ſitt/ zaur ko kas\nwarr nokauts tapt/ ta ka tas\nmirſt/ tas irr weens Slepkawe/\ntam buhs nokantam tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Affinu-Atreebejs laid\nnahwe to Slepkavu/ kad tas\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "wiẍam faſtohp buhs winna\nto nokaut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja wiꞥſch arridsan za\nEenaidu wiẍu gruhſch/ jeb\nWiltu koſabb us winnu mett/\nwiꞥſch nomirſt/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jeb ja tas wiẍuu za\nEenaidu ar ſawn Rohku ſitt/\ntas mirſt/ tam buhs nokauta-\ntapt/ jo wiꞥſch irr Slepkawe/ ta\nAffinu-Atreebejs laid to nokau-\nkad tas wiẍuu faſtohp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja wiꞥſch netiſchſch\nbes Eenaidu gruhſch/ jeb me\njebkuruu Rihku us winnu be\nWiltu;\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jeb kahdu Akmini/ za\nko kas warr nokauts tapt/ u\nwiẍuu leek kriſt/ un wiꞥſch\nne buhtu redſejis/ ta ka tas mirſ-\nkur wiꞥſch toinehr wiẍaa E-\nnaidneeks ne bija/ nedg win-\nNelaimi niekleja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad lai ta Draudse foht\nſtarp to Kaweju/ un ſtarp to A-\nfinu- Atreebeju pehz fawah-\nTeefahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un taiDraudsei buhs\nKaweju iſglahbt no ta Affinu-\nAtreebeja Rohkas/ un tai Dra-\ndset buhs wiẍuu lift atgreeste\nus to Gelbefchanas- Pilsfahti-\nkurp wiꞥſch bija behdsis/un eek-\nta buhs tam palikt/ teekams ta\nAugsts-Preesteris mirſt/ kas ar\nſwehtu Etji irr fiwaidihts tappi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ja tas Nokawejs i-\needains no tahs Rohbefchas fan\nGelbefchanas- Pilsfahta iseee-\nkurp wiꞥſch irr nobehdsis.\n"
    }
  ],
